    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras/521181a7fdfa1088ba9f7650b8b622f5.avif?t=1772104956\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras_big/521181a7fdfa1088ba9f7650b8b622f5.webp?t=1772104956 width=1560 height=218 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Seven hundred years</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>After</strong> a mysterious <strong>calamity</strong> drowned the world, you wash ashore with no memory. Storms rule the sky, twisted wildlife stalks the beaches, and rusted machines rot under the waves. To survive, you’ll rebuild a ship, sail between dangerous islands, and hunt an ancient <i>evil</i> poisoning the ocean. Along the way you’ll meet scattered survivors. Some helpful, some desperate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>Every island is its own challenge: new enemies, stranger terrain and fresh routes to carve through the wild.</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras/53d4691800a14763fbc006c4a2b85e0f.avif?t=1772104956\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras_big/53d4691800a14763fbc006c4a2b85e0f.webp?t=1772104956 width=1560 height=109 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras/e303d50a724edd7642ea35a15be99c08.poster.avif?t=1772104956\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras/e303d50a724edd7642ea35a15be99c08.webm?t=1772104956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras/e303d50a724edd7642ea35a15be99c08.mp4?t=1772104956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>⚓ Customizable ship (Exterior / Interior) ⚓</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🏝️ Crucial upgrades to reach distant islands 🏝️</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>👥 Can be crewed with up to 5 members 👥</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>💥Engine management, Harpoons and Cannons 💥</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🏃 Freely move around the deck 🏃</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras/d157107f50b1123ec7383b4c641ebb45.avif?t=1772104956\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras_big/d157107f50b1123ec7383b4c641ebb45.webp?t=1772104956 width=1560 height=109 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras/350839e37b8949c81fe6a60a3a73837d.poster.avif?t=1772104956\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras/350839e37b8949c81fe6a60a3a73837d.webm?t=1772104956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras/350839e37b8949c81fe6a60a3a73837d.mp4?t=1772104956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">🎯<strong> Stat-based RPG progression </strong>🎯</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🧛 Extensive Character Creator 🧛</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🏹 Melee, ranged, and magic abilities 🏹</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🛡️ 9 weapon classes &amp; 5 spell archetypes 🛡️</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🦘 Skill tree for builds and ability upgrades 🦘</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>👒 Armors and Hats with special properties 👒</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras/5858ff01de66b65127c8556c8962d49e.avif?t=1772104956\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras_big/5858ff01de66b65127c8556c8962d49e.webp?t=1772104956 width=1560 height=109 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras/61e39f843a28e785dab709f6e5042cfe.poster.avif?t=1772104956\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras/61e39f843a28e785dab709f6e5042cfe.webm?t=1772104956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras/61e39f843a28e785dab709f6e5042cfe.mp4?t=1772104956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🏝️ Abundance of handcrafted islands to discover🏝️</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🌵 Distinct biomes with unique environmental conditions 🌵</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🏰 New enemies, resources, and hazards on each island 🏰</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">🏛️  <strong>Islanders with real jobs, routines and priorities </strong>🏛️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras/b71dd25a89307838233ef1aa5f7894e8.avif?t=1772104956\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras_big/b71dd25a89307838233ef1aa5f7894e8.webp?t=1772104956 width=1560 height=109 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🤝 1–4 player online co-op 🤝</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>☠️ Solo or coordinate with friends to survive tougher regions ☠️</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras/0cdb51afb8baca40ebdf0fd3e0d6df4e.avif?t=1772104956\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras_big/0cdb51afb8baca40ebdf0fd3e0d6df4e.webp?t=1772104956 width=1560 height=109 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🏕️ Build camps to unlock crafting, footholds and faster travel 🏕️</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>⚔️ Upgrade weapons and armor using local resources ⚔️</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🔱 Manage travel, ship repairs, and supplies 🔱</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">💀 Poor preparation can kill you 💀</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras/df46cfaffbe0797acd67fba62273d89a.avif?t=1772104956\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877250/extras_big/df46cfaffbe0797acd67fba62273d89a.webp?t=1772104956 width=1560 height=109 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🎣 Fishing 🎣</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🐎 Tamable Horses and pets 🐎</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🏴‍☠️ Treasure hunting 🏴‍☠️</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
